      "text": "Real non-blocking issues identified: SRI missing on chatbot CDNs (fontawesome, marked, jquery 3.5.1, chart.js), jQuery 3.5.1 vulnerable (CVE-2020-11023), cross-domain JS. None block UAH deployment.",
